<i>of the noise,</i>

05:38.713 --> 05:41.632
<i>and soon came across a reminder
of a simpler time,</i>

05:41.716 --> 05:44.802
<i>and his dream of taking his son
on a scuba diving trip.</i>

05:47.013 --> 05:50.141
<i>He'd started the boy young,
getting him trained in</i>

05:50.224 --> 05:51.976
<i>- underwater communication.</i>
- Underwater communication.

05:52.060 --> 05:53.353
"Are you okay?"

